Recipe App
A Flutter-based Recipe App that allows users to explore and manage various recipes. This app provides a clean, intuitive interface for viewing detailed recipes, including ingredients and cooking steps, and browsing through a list of featured recipes.

Features
Browse Recipes: View a list of recipes with titles, descriptions, and images.
Recipe Details: Tap on a recipe to see detailed information, including ingredients and preparation steps.
User Interface: Uses Flutter widgets to create a responsive and user-friendly design.
Local Storage (Optional): Save favorite recipes locally for easy access.

Installation
Clone the Repository:
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/recipe-app.git

Navigate to the Project Directory:
cd recipe-app

Install Dependencies:
flutter pub get

Run the App:
flutter run

Technology Stack
Flutter: Framework for building the app.
Dart: Programming language used for Flutter development.
HTTP (optional): For fetching recipe data from an API (if applicable).

Usage
Home Screen: Displays a list of recipes. Tap on a recipe card to view details.
Recipe Detail Screen: Shows the full recipe, including ingredients and steps.

